		{"id":"b3ab2aac186e9b07","type":"text","text":"AI 推理（Inference）","x":1053,"y":715,"width":250,"height":50},
		{"id":"d45112ffa432ed12","type":"text","text":"**「記憶就是智慧」**\n\n- 沒有足夠的 HBM，AI 就會變慢（頻寬瓶頸）。\n- 沒有足夠的 DRAM，AI 就會變笨（失去上下文，產生幻覺）。\n- 沒有足夠的 NAND，AI 就會博而不精（失去深度知識與專業工具紀錄）。","x":1365,"y":842,"width":541,"height":212},
		{"id":"914c8022bbecdd12","type":"text","text":"AI 訓練（Training）","x":1053,"y":620,"width":250,"height":50},
		{"id":"6673a46d18a3e456","type":"text","text":"## GPU\n\n- **H100（Hopper 架構）**：搭載的是 80GB 的 **HBM2E**\n- **H200** 升級至 141GB的 **HBM3**\n- **B200（Blackwell 架構）**：搭載了 192GB 的 **HBM3E**","x":527,"y":583,"width":456,"height":224,"color":"4"},
